For a Lost Soldier;;1992;;Unrated;;Drama,Romance,War;;7.5;;Roeland Kerbosch;;Maarten Smit,Andrew Kelley,Jeroen Krabbé,Freark Smink,Elsje de Wijn,Derk-Jan Kroon,Wiendelt Hooijer,Iris Misset,Gineke de Jager,Tatum Dagelet,Marie-José Kouwenhoven,Valerie Valentine,William Sutton,Andrew Butling,Andrew Cassani,Moniek Kramer,Antoinette van Belle,Rients Gratama;;The story of a romantic relationship between a grown-up and a child. Set in the Netherlands near the end of WWII, the film is a flashback recalling an adolescent relationship between Jeroen and a Canadian soldier. A difficult subject handled with style and feeling.;;https://www.imdb.com/title/tt0108504/